description:
CarOutlet.eu – is a multi-functional online car auction system.

This product of CarOutlet Company is intended for all used car market participants – both for dealers and for car drivers.

We have developed this online car auction platform in order to enable you to buy high-quality cars directly from the leasing companies most conveniently and profitably at any time and from any location.

More than 10 years of experience in sales of used cars enabled us to become a trusted intermediary between car dealers and car traders.

Benefits of buying cars on CarOutlet:

Weekly update of cars for sale (more than 5,000 offers);
Favourable prices  - because you decide how much and for what car are you ready to pay;
All maintenance documents, maintenance history  are available – you can evaluate the quality of cars by themselves on the basis of objective data;
Quality pictures  of car interior and exterior;
You decide to purchase only on the basis of complete and reliable information from independent experts!
